      • scaleTo

        public void scaleTo(int width,
                    int height)
        Sets the scale to use for the TextureDrawables such that the image drawn is of a certain resolution.
        Parameters:
        width - The target width of the drawn image
        height - The target height of the drawn image

      • getTexturePath

        public abstract FilePath getTexturePath()
        This method should be implemented by subclasses to return a FilePath representing the location of the current texture. The file path should be relative to the "resources/assets/textures/" folder.
        Returns:
        The texture path of the current image to draw
